{
  "video_id": "ZdDjexbxVzM",
  "title": "Allan Adams: The discovery that could rewrite physics",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12928.0,
      "end_time": 16420.0,
      "text": "If you look deep into the night sky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16420.0,
      "end_time": 18360.0,
      "text": "you see stars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18360.0,
      "end_time": 20608.0,
      "text": "and if you look further, you see more stars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20608.0,
      "end_time": 22767.0,
      "text": "and further, galaxies, and  further, more galaxies."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22767.0,
      "end_time": 26640.0,
      "text": "But if you keep looking further and further,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26640.0,
      "end_time": 29756.0,
      "text": "eventually you see nothing for a long while,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29756.0,
      "end_time": 34218.0,
      "text": "and then finally you see a faint, fading afterglow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34218.0,
      "end_time": 37242.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s the afterglow of the Big Bang."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37242.0,
      "end_time": 40590.0,
      "text": "Now, the Big Bang was an era in the early universe"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40590.0,
      "end_time": 42230.0,
      "text": "when everything we see in the night sky"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42230.0,
      "end_time": 44640.0,
      "text": "was condensed into an incredibly small,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44640.0,
      "end_time": 48966.0,
      "text": "incredibly hot, incredibly roiling mass,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 48966.0,
      "end_time": 51658.0,
      "text": "and from it sprung everything we see."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 51658.0,
      "end_time": 54517.0,
      "text": "Now, we&#39;ve mapped that afterglow"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54517.0,
      "end_time": 56196.0,
      "text": "with great precision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56196.0,
      "end_time": 58239.0,
      "text": "and when I say we, I mean people who aren&#39;t me."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58240.0,
      "end_time": 60116.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve mapped the afterglow"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60116.0,
      "end_time": 61438.0,
      "text": "with spectacular precision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61438.0,
      "end_time": 62986.0,
      "text": "and one of the shocks about it"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 62986.0,
      "end_time": 65932.0,
      "text": "is that it&#39;s almost completely uniform."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65932.0,
      "end_time": 67890.0,
      "text": "Fourteen billion light years that way"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67890.0,
      "end_time": 69750.0,
      "text": "and 14 billion light years that way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 69750.0,
      "end_time": 71158.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s the same temperature."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71158.0,
      "end_time": 74472.0,
      "text": "Now it&#39;s been 14 billion years"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74472.0,
      "end_time": 76289.0,
      "text": "since that Big Bang,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76290.0,
      "end_time": 78762.0,
      "text": "and so it&#39;s got faint and cold."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78762.0,
      "end_time": 81700.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s now 2.7 degrees."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81700.0,
      "end_time": 83350.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not exactly 2.7 degrees."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83350.0,
      "end_time": 85643.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s only 2.7 degrees to about"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85644.0,
      "end_time": 87486.0,
      "text": "10 parts in a million."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87486.0,
      "end_time": 88480.0,
      "text": "Over here, it&#39;s a little hotter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 88480.0,
      "end_time": 90348.0,
      "text": "and over there, it&#39;s a little cooler,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 90348.0,
      "end_time": 93436.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s incredibly important to everyone in this room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 93436.0,
      "end_time": 95160.0,
      "text": "because where it was a little hotter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 95160.0,
      "end_time": 96856.0,
      "text": "there was a little more stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 96856.0,
      "end_time": 98422.0,
      "text": "and where there was a little more stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 98423.0,
      "end_time": 100392.0,
      "text": "we have galaxies and clusters of galaxies"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 100392.0,
      "end_time": 101643.0,
      "text": "and superclusters"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 101644.0,
      "end_time": 104352.0,
      "text": "and all the structure you see in the cosmos."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 104352.0,
      "end_time": 107464.0,
      "text": "And those small, little, inhomogeneities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 107464.0,
      "end_time": 109746.0,
      "text": "20 parts in a million,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 109746.0,
      "end_time": 112500.0,
      "text": "those were formed by quantum mechanical wiggles"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 112500.0,
      "end_time": 114308.0,
      "text": "in that early universe that were stretched"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 114308.0,
      "end_time": 116587.0,
      "text": "across the size of the entire cosmos."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 116587.0,
      "end_time": 118301.0,
      "text": "That is spectacular,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 118301.0,
      "end_time": 119966.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s not what they found on Monday;"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 119966.0,
      "end_time": 122200.0,
      "text": "what they found on Monday is cooler."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 122200.0,
      "end_time": 124268.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s what they found on Monday:"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 124268.0,
      "end_time": 127771.0,
      "text": "Imagine you take a bell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 127771.0,
      "end_time": 129382.0,
      "text": "and you whack the bell with a hammer."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 129382.0,
      "end_time": 131580.0,
      "text": "What happens? It rings."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 131580.0,
      "end_time": 133266.0,
      "text": "But if you wait, that ringing fades"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 133266.0,
      "end_time": 134886.0,
      "text": "and fades and fades"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 134886.0,
      "end_time": 136828.0,
      "text": "until you don&#39;t notice it anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 136828.0,
      "end_time": 139476.0,
      "text": "Now, that early universe was incredibly dense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 139476.0,
      "end_time": 141555.0,
      "text": "like a metal, way denser,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 141555.0,
      "end_time": 143960.0,
      "text": "and if you hit it, it would ring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 143960.0,
      "end_time": 145823.0,
      "text": "but the thing ringing would be"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 145823.0,
      "end_time": 147911.0,
      "text": "the structure of space-time itself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 147911.0,
      "end_time": 150727.0,
      "text": "and the hammer would be quantum mechanics."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 150727.0,
      "end_time": 152658.0,
      "text": "What they found on Monday"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 152658.0,
      "end_time": 155190.0,
      "text": "was evidence of the ringing"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 155200.0,
      "end_time": 157335.0,
      "text": "of the space-time of the early universe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 157335.0,
      "end_time": 159440.0,
      "text": "what we call gravitational waves"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 159440.0,
      "end_time": 160960.0,
      "text": "from the fundamental era,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 160960.0,
      "end_time": 162935.0,
      "text": "and here&#39;s how they found it."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 162935.0,
      "end_time": 165700.0,
      "text": "Those waves have long since faded."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 165700.0,
      "end_time": 166495.0,
      "text": "If you go for a walk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 166495.0,
      "end_time": 168830.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t wiggle."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 168830.0,
      "end_time": 170831.0,
      "text": "Those gravitational waves in the structure of space"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 170831.0,
      "end_time": 173605.0,
      "text": "are totally invisible for all practical purposes."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 173605.0,
      "end_time": 176509.0,
      "text": "But early on, when the universe was making"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 176509.0,
      "end_time": 178879.0,
      "text": "that last afterglow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 178879.0,
      "end_time": 180436.0,
      "text": "the gravitational waves"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 180437.0,
      "end_time": 183300.0,
      "text": "put little twists in the structure"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 183300.0,
      "end_time": 184827.0,
      "text": "of the light that we see."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 184827.0,
      "end_time": 187793.0,
      "text": "So by looking at the night sky deeper and deeper --"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 187793.0,
      "end_time": 190431.0,
      "text": "in fact, these guys spent three years on the South Pole"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 190431.0,
      "end_time": 193200.0,
      "text": "looking straight up through the coldest, clearest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 193200.0,
      "end_time": 195370.0,
      "text": "cleanest air they possibly could find"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 195370.0,
      "end_time": 197799.0,
      "text": "looking deep into the night sky and studying"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 197799.0,
      "end_time": 201175.0,
      "text": "that glow and looking for the faint twists"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 201175.0,
      "end_time": 203523.0,
      "text": "which are the symbol, the signal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 203523.0,
      "end_time": 205343.0,
      "text": "of gravitational waves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 205343.0,
      "end_time": 207684.0,
      "text": "the ringing of the early universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 207684.0,
      "end_time": 209471.0,
      "text": "And on Monday, they announced"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 209471.0,
      "end_time": 211215.0,
      "text": "that they had found it."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 211215.0,
      "end_time": 213642.0,
      "text": "And the thing that&#39;s so spectacular about that to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 213642.0,
      "end_time": 216390.0,
      "text": "is not just the ringing, though that is awesome."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 216390.0,
      "end_time": 217748.0,
      "text": "The thing that&#39;s totally amazing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 217748.0,
      "end_time": 219850.0,
      "text": "the reason I&#39;m on this stage, is because"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 219850.0,
      "end_time": 223317.0,
      "text": "what that tells us is something deep about the early universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 223318.0,
      "end_time": 224982.0,
      "text": "It tells us that we"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 224982.0,
      "end_time": 226418.0,
      "text": "and everything we see around us"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 226418.0,
      "end_time": 229372.0,
      "text": "are basically one large bubble --"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 229372.0,
      "end_time": 231128.0,
      "text": "and this is the idea of inflation—"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 231128.0,
      "end_time": 235190.0,
      "text": "one large bubble surrounded by something else."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 235200.0,
      "end_time": 237150.0,
      "text": "This isn&#39;t conclusive evidence for inflation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 237150.0,
      "end_time": 239324.0,
      "text": "but anything that isn&#39;t inflation that explains this"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 239324.0,
      "end_time": 240641.0,
      "text": "will look the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 240641.0,
      "end_time": 242286.0,
      "text": "This is a theory, an idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 242286.0,
      "end_time": 243510.0,
      "text": "that has been around for a while,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 243510.0,
      "end_time": 245234.0,
      "text": "and we never thought we we&#39;d really see it."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 245235.0,
      "end_time": 247730.0,
      "text": "For good reasons, we thought we&#39;d never see"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 247730.0,
      "end_time": 249321.0,
      "text": "killer evidence, and this is killer evidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 249321.0,
      "end_time": 251331.0,
      "text": "But the really crazy idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 251331.0,
      "end_time": 254363.0,
      "text": "is that our bubble is just one bubble"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 254363.0,
      "end_time": 258988.0,
      "text": "in a much larger, roiling pot of universal stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 258988.0,
      "end_time": 260815.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re never going to see the stuff outside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 260815.0,
      "end_time": 263389.0,
      "text": "but by going to the South Pole and spending three years"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 263389.0,
      "end_time": 265949.0,
      "text": "looking at the detailed structure of the night sky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 265949.0,
      "end_time": 267805.0,
      "text": "we can figure out"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 267805.0,
      "end_time": 270895.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re probably in a universe that looks kind of like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 270895.0,
      "end_time": 273317.0,
      "text": "And that amazes me."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 273317.0,
      "end_time": 274653.0,
      "text": "Thanks a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 274653.0,
      "end_time": 277589.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}